{"tid":1926940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港府向美國、英國、愛爾蘭發出紅色外遊警示","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T13:35:03.000Z","uid":184261,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb2d4812603274b7c3b13137021d2223ecd0e2d","tid":1926940,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"Source: RTHK iCable"},{"pid":"ad19949b3af4ff1b3b6869a3000f46eee2976b9f","tid":1926940,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"因應香港特別行政區政府今日（三月十五日）公布，為應對2019冠狀病毒病的最新疫情，對愛爾蘭、英國及美國發出紅色外遊警示，衞生署將對由該三個國家以及現時紅色外遊警示仍然生效的埃及抵港的人士加強衞生檢疫安排，要求有關人士接受家居強制檢疫。全球各地的疫情變化急劇，衞生署強烈呼籲市民應避免所有非必要的外遊計劃。<br />\n <br />\n  由三月十九日零時零分起，衞生署港口衞生科人員會根據《預防及控制疾病規例》（第599A章），要求所有於抵港前14日曾到愛爾蘭、英國、美國或埃及的人士（不論是否香港居民）接受家居強制檢疫。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/15/P2020031500620.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F15%2FP2020031500620.htm&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=91aadd6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/15/P2020031500620.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3fa2da5d4e85683b22bc8dbb1aa9e06992705a9e","tid":1926940,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"可冇以對全世界發出黑色旅遊警示"},{"pid":"466d81ae5d98822c18ce4cfb4386d081d40aa9d1","tid":1926940,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"不過堅持唔封深圳灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d4d1938d8c496be27b91dec741c7e3f18d36c9","tid":1926940,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa2da5d4e85683b22bc8dbb1aa9e06992705a9e","tid":1926940,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"可冇以對全世界發出黑色旅遊警示"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"Except Chi-nazi <img src=\"/assets